title: OM SHANTI OM 360px (2007) Hindi...TECH-HACKERS...
description:
OM SHANTI OM 360px (2007) Hindi...TECH-HACKERS...
                   =================================================
In the 1970s, Om, an aspiring actor, is murdered, but is immediately reincarnated into the present day. He attempts to discover the mystery of his demise and find Shanti, the love of his previous life.


Director: Farah Khan

Writers: Farah Khan (story), Mushtaq Sheikh (screenplay),

Stars: Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone, Arjun Rampal and crew
